teraction.%20I%20need%20a%20bit%20of%20what%20your%20background%20is%2C%20what%20your%20name%20is%2C%20and%20what%20your%20interest%20in%20art%20is.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20a%20few%20years%20after%20COVID%2C%20I%20would%20give%20students%20the%20questions%20that%20we%20were%20going%20to%20discuss%20and%20have%20them%20write%20things%20down.%20Then%2C%20you're%20reading%20it%20instead%20of%20saying%20it.%20That%20would%20be%20helpful%2C%20though%20sometimes%20they%20wouldn't%20write%20anything.%20That's%20when%20I%20would%20just%20be%20like%2C%20I%20don't%20really%20know%20what%20to%20do.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20just%20don't%20participate%20%E2%80%94%20I%20expect%20that%20more%20from%20middle%20school%20and%20high%20school%20students.%20Those%20students%20often%20don't%20want%20to%20be%20there%2C%20but%20they%20have%20to%20be.%20In%20my%20case%2C%20these%20were%20college%20students.%20I%20was%20like%2C%20%26quot%3BYou're%20choosing%20to%20be%20here%2C%20and%20you're%20paying%20to%20be%20here.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20what%20was%20always%20hard%20for%20me.%20I%20want%20you%20to%20have%20the%20experience%20that%20you%20want.%20And%20if%20you%20won't%20tell%20me%2C%20if%20you%20won't%20interact%20with%20me%2C%20then%20I%20don't%20know%20what%20your%20values%20are%20or%20what%20kind%20of%20interaction%20you%20want.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2211c1a94f-b297-4526-85a7-03c2a240bee6%5C%22%3EWhy%20videos%20feel%20more%20comfortable%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20need%20students%20to%20ask%20questions%20when%20they%20don't%20know%20what%20to%20do.%20Sometimes%20it's%20good%20for%20them%20to%20say%2C%20%26quot%3BHey%2C%20I'm%20a%20little%20lost.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20COVID%2C%20when%20everything%20was%20online%2C%20I%20made%20video%20versions%20of%20a%20lot%20of%20my%20in-class%20demonstrations%20and%20lectures.%20I%20still%20made%20those%20videos%20after%20students%20came%20back%20to%20class.%20Yet%20the%20in-class%20demo%20was%20better%20because%20you%20can%20ask%20questions%2C%20and%20I%20can%20talk%20to%20you%20more%20specifically%20about%20what%20I'm%20doing.%20But%20I%20would%20find%20that%2C%20instead%20of%20asking%20questions%20or%20asking%20me%20to%20clarify%20things%2C%20I%20would%20have%20students%20watching%20the%20videos%20during%20class.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20would%20even%20have%20students%20watch%20the%20video%20of%20me%20doing%20a%20demonstration%20while%20I%20am%20doing%20that%20same%20demonstration%20in%20class.%20It's%20mind-blowing%20to%20me%2C%20but%20it%20almost%20just%20felt%20more%20comfortable%20for%20them%20to%20look%20at%20that%20on%20a%20screen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20really%20think%20that%20those%20few%20years%20of%20being%20on%20Zoom%20for%20everything%20affected%20that%20entire%20generation's%20social%20skills.%20I%20don't%20know%20if%20that's%20a%20good%20thing%20or%20a%20bad%20thing.%20The%20future%20is%20more%20and%20more%20online.%20A%20lot%20of%20them%20are%20going%20to%20be%20working%20online%2C%20and%20so%20navigating%20online%20social%20spheres%20and%20Zoom%20work%20life%20is%20important.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20value%20of%20being%20in%20class%20is%20social%20interaction%2C%20getting%20specific%20questions%20answered%2C%20and%20getting%20an%20education%20that%20is%20specific%20to%20you.%20If%20you're%20in%20the%20class%2C%20watching%20a%20video%20of%20the%20class%20%E2%80%94%20it%20really%20just%20broke%20my%20brain%20a%20little%20bit%20to%20see%20that%20happen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20way%20education%20is%20now%2C%20most%20information%20that%20you're%20going%20to%20get%20in%20school%2C%20you%20can%20get%20online.%20The%20value%20of%20going%20to%20an%20educational%20institution%20is%20to%20have%20that%20education%20tailored%20toward%20you.%20The%20reason%20you're%20there%20is%20for%20you%20to%20work%20on%20your%20own%20self-expression%2C%20your%20own%20way%20that%20you%20navigate%20the%20world%2C%20and%20having%20someone%20looking%20at%20what%20you%20do%20and%20tailoring%20the%20education%20toward%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20colleges%20and%20universities%2C%20what%20you%20pay%20for%20is%20the%20way%20the%20information%20is%20presented%2C%20and%20for%20the%20interaction%20that%20you%20have%20with%20professors%20and%20with%20experts%2C%20and%20to%20have%20opportunities%20to%20meet%20people%20and%20to%20just%20have%20experiences%20that%20you%20wouldn't%20be%20able%20to%20have%20otherwise.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22fd71cce6-1dd9-4f0a-9d52-67d967ca3a91%5C%22%3EA%20tarnished%20experience%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20group%20of%20students%20had%20a%20really%20bad%20situation%20because%20of%20COVID.%20For%20some%20of%20them%2C%20their%20high%20school%20experience%20was%20really%20tarnished%2C%20and%2C%20for%20some%2C%20their%20college%20experience%20was%20tarnished.%20Their%20education%20was%20lacking%2C%20and%20their%20social%20interaction%20was%20lacking.%20Their%20ability%20to%20enter%20the%20workforce%20was%20affected.%20It%20really%20just%20negatively%20impacted%20every%20social%20aspect%20of%20their%20lives.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20know%20how%20much%20COVID%20negatively%20impacted%20my%20mental%20health%2C%20and%20I%20am%20far%20past%20my%20most-formative%20years.%20So%2C%20there's%20no%20way%20that%20couldn't%20have%20a%20huge%20impact%20on%20their%20mental%20health.%20There's%20all%20this%20conversation%20about%20them%20staring%20at%20you%20in%20a%20social%20interaction%20when%20it's%20just%20like%2C%20the%20world%20failed%20them.%20Society%20failed%20them%20in%20a%20major%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20larger%20discussion%20should%20be%20that%20we%20need%20to%20figure%20out%20better%20ways%20for%20all%20of%20us%20to%20have%20access%20to%20the%20mental%20health%20services%20that%20we%20need%2C%20because%20I%20don't%20think%20we%20have%20recovered%20from%20COVID.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%2F%2Fembed.typeform.com%2Fnext%2Fembed.js%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5