ith%20the%20matter%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20firm%20has%20been%20expanding%20alternative%20investments%2C%20including%20establishing%20a%20new%20group%20to%20focus%20on%20private%20lending.%20Such%20loans%2C%20which%20are%20often%20made%20with%20money%20raised%20from%20investors%2C%20have%20become%20a%20hot%20topic%20of%20growth%20in%20private%20equity%20and%20beyond.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECEO%20David%20Solomon%20said%20Wednesday%20on%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoldman-sachs-second-quarter-earnings-david-solomon-merger-acquisitions-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecall%20with%20shareholders%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20AWM%20division%20raised%20%2418%20billion%20for%20its%20alternative%20investment%20funds%20last%20quarter%2C%20including%20growth%20equity%20and%20secondaries%2C%20which%20involves%20investing%20in%20discarded%20stakes%20of%20buyout%20funds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20year's%20private%20equity%20recruiting%20sprint%20has%20been%20in%20limbo%20without%20clear%20indications%20as%20to%20when%20it%20will%20start.%20Shortly%20after%20JPMorgan's%20letter%20banning%20its%20bankers%20from%20future-dated%20jobs%2C%20a%20series%20of%20large%20private%20equity%20firms%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0including%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgeneral-atlantic-halts-2027-private-equity-recruiting-apollo-jpmorgan-oncycle-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EGeneral%20Atlantic%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapollo-private-equity-recruiting-letter-2027-associates-oncycle-jpmorgan-chase-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EApollo%20Global%20Management%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftpg-private-equity-recruiting-memo-oncycle-2027-associates-apollo-ga-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ETPG%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0said%20they%20would%20sit%20out%20poaching%20incoming%20investment%20bankers%20until%20next%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20past%20years%2C%20the%20private%20equity%20recruiting%20rush%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fprivate-equity-recruiting-apollo-jpmorgan-reactions-junior-bankers-recruiters-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ekicked%20off%3C%2Fa%3E%20during%20the%20peak%20summer%20months%2C%20upsetting%20banks%20by%20recruiting%20junior%20talent%20for%20future-dated%20jobs%20before%20they've%20even%20had%20a%20chance%20to%20test%20drive%20a%20career%20in%20investment%20banking.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20the%20full%20memo%20from%20Goldman's%20global%20banking%20and%20markets%20cohead%20Dan%20Dees%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cblockquote%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cstrong%3EJuly%2017%2C%202025%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cstrong%3EExploring%20Career%20Opportunities%20Across%20GBM%20and%20AWM%20at%20Goldman%20Sachs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3ETime%20moves%20fast%20at%20Goldman%20Sachs%20%E2%80%94%20congratulations%20on%20passing%20the%20halfway%20mark%20of%20your%20internships.%20I%20wanted%20to%20share%20an%20important%20update%20with%20you%20on%20career%20opportunities%20we%20offer%20at%20the%20firm.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EAs%20someone%20who%20started%20his%20career%20at%20the%20firm%20thinking%20it%20would%20be%20a%20two-year%20stint%20%E2%80%94%20and%20then%20stayed%20for%20at%20least%2012%20jobs%2C%20eight%20cities%2C%20and%20many%20years%20more%20%E2%80%94%20I%20know%20how%20important%20it%20is%20to%20build%20a%20career%20that%20is%20rich%20and%20rewarding.%20As%20Ashok%20and%20I%20said%20in%20June%2C%20we%20hire%20people%20based%20on%20their%20curiosity%20and%20drive%2C%20and%20so%20it%20seems%20fair%20some%20of%20you%20might%20consider%20working%20for%20other%20great%20teams%20and%20firms%2C%20many%20of%20whom%20are%20our%20clients%2C%20too.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EI%20also%20understand%20pressure%2C%20and%20what%20it%20means%20to%20have%20made%20it%20this%20far.%20We%20hire%20the%20best%20and%20brightest%2C%20and%20many%20of%20you%20have%20been%20working%20hard%20for%20most%20of%20your%20academic%20careers.%20After%20so%20many%20years%20of%20effort%20you%20will%20feel%20comfort%20in%20having%20your%20career%20mapped%20out.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EI%20also%20know%20few%20companies%20offer%20a%20better%20platform%20and%20more%20exciting%20career%20paths%20than%20Goldman%20Sachs.%20Whether%20it's%20a%20switch%20from%20leading%20the%20financing%20group%20in%20Japan%20to%20global%20TMT%20coverage%20in%20San%20Francisco%20(as%20I%20did)%2C%20or%20from%20banking%20to%20trading%20to%20asset%20management%20(like%20fellow%20division%20head%20Marc%20Nachmann)%2C%20the%20possibilities%2C%20and%20offices%20around%20the%20world%20from%20which%20to%20explore%20them%2C%20are%20almost%20endless.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3ETo%20that%20end%2C%20I'm%20pleased%20to%20share%20that%20we%20will%20introduce%20an%20additional%20early%20entry%20point%20for%20those%20of%20you%20interested%20in%20exploring%20buyside%20careers%2C%20in%20partnership%20with%20our%20AWM%20colleagues.%20The%20program%20will%20offer%20a%20select%20group%20of%20applicants%20a%20full-time%20offer%20to%20join%20Investment%20Banking%2C%20followed%20by%20mobility%20to%20Asset%20Management%20after%20two%20years.%20Register%20your%20interest%20and%20your%20business%20unit%20managers%20will%20let%20you%20know%20next%20steps.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EOf%20course%2C%20for%20those%20of%20you%20committed%20to%20banking%20%E2%80%94%20I%20would%20encourage%20it!%20%E2%80%94%20you%20will%20have%20opportunities%20as%20you%20become%20more%20senior%20to%20stay%20in%20your%20existing%20teams%20or%20participate%20in%20our%20very%20own%20mobility%20program.%20You%20will%20also%20be%20able%20to%20register%20an%20interest%20to%20join%20Asset%20Management%2C%20and%20teams%20across%20the%20firm%2C%20at%20other%20future%20moments%20throughout%20your%20career.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EOur%20goal%20with%20such%20a%20talented%20cohort%20is%20to%20offer%20the%20options%20to%20you.%20I%20might%20be%20a%20little%20biased%2C%20but%20the%20path%20you%20find%20yourself%20on%20at%20Goldman%20Sachs%20might%20just%20be%20the%20one%20that%20keeps%20you%20here%20many%2C%20many%20years%20later.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EDan%20Dees%3C%2Fsection%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EHave%20a%20tip%3F%20Contact%20this%20reporter%20via%20email%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Aralexander%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Eralexander%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20or%20SMS%2FSignal%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22tel%3A561-247-5758%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3E561-247-5758%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%20Use%20a%20personal%20email%20address%20and%20a%20nonwork%20device%3B%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finsider-guide-to-securely-sharing-whistleblower-information-about-powerful-institutions-2021-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Ehere's%20our%20guide%20to%20sharing%20information%20securely%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoldman-sachs-letter-interns-asset-management-private-equity-talent-wars-2025-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1752765048000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F687907b03d5881a51c1d815b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoldman-sachs-letter-interns-asset-management-private-equity-talent-wars-2025-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Goldman%20Sachs%20has%20a%20new%20plan%20to%20keep%20junior%20talent%20from%20defecting%20to%20private%20equity%3A%20Offering%20them%20buyside%20jobs%20within%20the%20bank.%20See%20the%20memo.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ralexan