ssinsider.com%2Ftell-dell-annual-survey-results-show-employees-frustration-rto-push-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ethe%20results%20weren't%20great%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20year%2C%20they're%20worse.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Tuesday%2C%3Cem%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3EJenn%20Saavedra%2C%20Dell's%20chief%20HR%20officer%2C%20announced%20that%20the%20employee%20net%20promoter%20score%20(eNPS)%20%E2%80%94%20an%20industry-standard%20measure%20of%20employee%20satisfaction%20%E2%80%94%20had%20fallen%20to%2032%2C%20according%20to%20a%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Etranscript%20of%20an%20internal%20video%20update%20obtained%20by%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20results%20mark%20a%20double-digit%20drop%20in%20the%20eNPS%20for%20the%20second%20year%20running%20at%20Dell%20%E2%80%94%20it%20fell%20from%2063%20to%2048%20in%202024%20%E2%80%94%20and%20an%20almost%2050%25%20decline%20in%20two%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESaavedra%20said%20the%20eNPS%20score%20was%20%26quot%3Bbelow%20the%20benchmark%20we%20do%20aim%20to%20achieve%2C%20and%20we%20take%20that%20seriously%2C%26quot%3B%20per%20the%20transcript.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESaavedra%20told%20employees%20that%20Dell%20had%20been%20%26quot%3Bnavigating%20a%20lot%20of%20change%20both%20within%20the%20company%20and%20in%20the%20broader%20environment%2C%26quot%3B%20adding%20that%20the%20pace%20and%20scale%20of%20the%20change%20has%20been%20%26quot%3Ba%20lot.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDell%20declined%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20BI%20for%20this%20story.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224f40c8b2-a7d1-426d-8075-15c0b9d3c478%5C%22%3E'Tell%20Dell'%20survey%20results%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20eNPS%20score%20is%20the%20key%20metric%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Femployees-sick-tired-engagement-surveys-managers-happiness-hr-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EDell's%20annual%20survey%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20called%20%26quot%3BTell%20Dell.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20question%20asks%20employees%20to%20rank%20how%20likely%20they%20would%20be%20to%20recommend%20Dell%20as%20a%20great%20place%20to%20work%20to%20someone%20they%20know%20on%20a%20scale%20from%201%20to%2010.%20The%20eNPS%20is%20calculated%20as%20the%20percentage%20of%20promoters%20minus%20the%20percentage%20of%20detractors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFour%20Dell%20employees%20who%20spoke%20to%20BI%20about%20the%20Tell%20Dell%20results%20raised%20factors%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdell-return-to-office-five-days-week-rto-michael-dell-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EDell's%20RTO%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdell-workers-layoffs-reaction-ai-restructuring-jobs-tech-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eongoing%20layoffs%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20fatigue%20with%20the%20company's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdell-layoffs-ai-strategy-workers-more-effective-jobs-fulfilling-2024-8%23%3A~%3Atext%3DDell%2520is%2520putting%2520AI%2520at%2Crestructuring%2520that%2520includes%2520major%2520layoffs.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAI%20push%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20a%20shift%20in%20culture%20as%20reasons%20for%20the%20eNPS%20decline.%20They%20spoke%20on%20the%20condition%20of%20anonymity.%20BI%20has%20verified%20their%20identities%20and%20employment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20been%20a%20general%20decrease%20in%20trust%20with%20all%20the%20regular%20layoffs%20and%20feeling%20like%20the%20company%20isn't%20listening%20to%20employee%20concerns%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20one%20employee%20who%20is%20based%20at%20Dell's%20Round%20Rock%20headquarters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20person%20said%20that%20office%20conditions%2C%20such%20as%20%26quot%3Bnoisy%20rooms%20and%20desks%20that%20feel%20temporary%2C%26quot%3B%20were%20also%20contributing%20to%20low%20morale.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMost%20people%20I%20know%20are%20not%20feeling%20secure%20in%20their%20jobs%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dell%20Technologies%20building%20in%20Round%20Rock%2C%20Texas%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65c4da0443bb77284ba4d987%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22683%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDell's%20headquarters%20in%20Round%20Rock%2C%20Texas.%3Cp%3EBrandon%20Bell%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20more%20negative%20on%20my%20Tell%20Dell%20than%20I%20have%20ever%20been%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20Dell%20engineer%20who%20has%20been%20at%20the%20company%20for%20more%20than%20eight%20years%2C%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20engineer%20said%20they%20felt%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ethe%20company's%20RTO%20push%20and%20layoffs%20had%20damaged%20Dell's%20reputation%20as%20a%20good%20place%20to%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPreviously%2C%20managers%20were%20flexible%2C%20workforce%20reductions%20were%20rare%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eand%20employees%20enjoyed%20a%20good%20work-life%20balance%2C%20the%20engineer%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20said%20they%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Efelt%20company%20culture%20had%20changed%20as%20they%20had%20been%20%26quot%3Bgradually%20and%20with%20decreasing%20compassion%20and%20understanding%20forced%20back%20into%20the%20office.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20constant%20layoffs%20are%20just%20the%20cherry%20on%20top%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20engineer%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDell%20has%20been%20steadily%20ramping%20up%20its%20RTO%20policy%20since%20February%202024%2C%20when%20it%20asked%20all%20US%20employees%20to%20classify%20themselves%20as%20either%20hybrid%20or%20remote%20%E2%80%94%20roughly%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-dell-workers-reject-return-to-office-hybrid-work-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E50%25%20opted%20to%20stay%20remote%3C%2Fa%3E.%20In%20September%2C%20the%20sales%20team%20was%20called%20back%20to%20the%20office%20five%20days%20a%20week%2C%20and%20in%20January%2C%20all%20staff%20living%20near%20a%20Dell%20office%20were%20told%20they%20were%20required%20to%20be%20in%20five%20days%20a%20week%20from%20March.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdell-business-trends-of-the-year-rto-ai-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EVivek%20Mohindra%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Dell's%20senior%20vice%20president%20of%20corporate%20strategy%2C%20previously%20told%20BI%20that%20having%20staff%20in%20the%20office%20brought%20%26quot%3Bhuge%20benefits%2C%26quot%3B%20including%20%26quot%3Blearning%20from%20each%20other%2C%20training%2C%20and%20mentorship.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20all%20the%20technology%20in%20the%20world%2C%20nothing%20is%20faster%20than%20the%20speed%20of%20human%20interaction%2C%26quot%3B%20CEO%20Michael%20Dell%20told%20staff%20in%20an%20internal%20memo%20when%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdell-return-to-office-five-days-week-rto-michael-dell-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ethe%205-day%20RTO%20was%20announced%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAlongside%20the%20RTO%20push%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3EDell's%20workforce%20has%20shrunk%20significantly%20in%20recent%20years.%20An%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdell-employee-numbers-decline-by-25000-since-2023-rto-layoffs-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ESEC%20filing%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20March%20showed%20that%20the%20company's%20staff%20numbers%20have%20fallen%20by%2025%2C000%20in%20the%20last%20two%20years%20%E2%80%94%20a%2019%25%20reduction.%20As%20of%20January%202025%2C%20Dell%20employs%20108%2C000%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20tech%20support%20employee%20based%20at%20the%20company's%20RoundRock%20headquarters%20said%20the%20fall%20in%20head%20count%20had%20led%20to%20increased%20workloads%20on%20their%20team.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20the%20ongoing%20workforce%20reductions%20have%20held%20back%20internal%