that%20the%20Federal%20Student%20Aid%20office%20%E2%80%94%20which%20the%20report%20said%20administers%20over%20%24120%20billion%20in%20grants%20and%20student%20loans%20annually%20%E2%80%94%20would%20lose%20staff.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20American%20Council%20on%20Education%20told%20Warren%20that%20%26quot%3Bdelayed%20funding%2C%20especially%20in%20the%20instances%20of%20student%20financial%20aid%2C%20can%20result%20in%20the%20inability%20of%20students%20to%20enroll%20for%20classes%20and%20persist%20through%20to%20completion%20in%20a%20timely%20fashion%2C%20causing%20them%20to%20take%20on%20more%20student%20loan%20debt%20to%20complete%20their%20degrees.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDelays%20in%20receiving%20federal%20student%20aid%20could%20also%20lead%20some%20students%20to%20turn%20to%20private%20lenders%3B%20the%20NEA%20said%20that%20private%20student%20loans%20often%20have%20riskier%20terms%20and%20can%20lead%20to%20predatory%20lending.%20They%20might%20be%20the%20only%20route%20students%20have%20if%20they%20cannot%20receive%20federal%20student%20loans%20promptly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20report%20comes%20amid%20a%20summer%20of%20changes%20for%20student-loan%20borrowers%20and%20education%20overall.%20The%20administration%20announced%20in%20April%20that%20it%20was%20restarting%20collections%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-reinstating-penalties-default-student-loan-borrowers-treasury-offset-program-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edefaulted%20student%20loans%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20a%20five-year%20pause.%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsave-plan-student-loan-borrowers-when-does-interest-restart-trump-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EInterest%20charges%20resumed%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0on%208%20million%20borrowers'%20balances%20on%20August%201%20after%20a%20year%20on%20pause%2C%20and%20Trump's%20spending%20bill%2C%20which%20he%20signed%20into%20law%20on%20July%204%2C%20codified%20significant%20ch