ner%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F91635%2Fletters-of-love-syrian-refugee-kids-postcards%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erefugee%20camps%3C%2Fa%3E%20seemed%20counterintuitive.%20Jhingran%2C%20however%2C%20thought%20differently%3A%20%E2%80%9CI%20believed%20that%20bringing%20back%20peace%20and%20a%20literacy%20campaign%20should%20be%20woven%20together.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Fdhir-jhingran-foundational-literacy-2-1752495639.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22At%20the%20Language%20and%20Learning%20Foundation%2C%20multilingualism%20becomes%20a%20tool%20rather%20than%20a%20spoke%20in%20the%20wheel%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Fdhir-jhingran-foundational-literacy-2-1752495639.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Fdhir-jhingran-foundational-literacy-2-1752495639-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Fdhir-jhingran-foundational-literacy-2-1752495639-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Fdhir-jhingran-foundational-literacy-2-1752495639-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Fdhir-jhingran-foundational-literacy-2-1752495639-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-469657%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAt%20the%20Language%20and%20Learning%20Foundation%2C%20multilingualism%20becomes%20a%20tool%20rather%20than%20a%20spoke%20in%20the%20wheel%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElaborating%20on%20the%20literacy%20campaign%2C%20he%20shares%20how%20it%20targeted%20adults%20aged%2015%20to%2045%20years%2C%20intending%20to%20help%20them%20learn%20to%20read%20and%20write.%20Teaching%20adults%20meant%20recalibrating%20the%20fundamental%20yardsticks%20of%20basic%20education.%20The%20goal%20was%20hefty%2C%20but%20not%20impossible.%20Jhingran%20explains%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20created%20a%20team%20of%203%2C000%20volunteers%20in%20the%20district.%20Mainly%20youth%20%E2%80%94%20young%20women%20%E2%80%94%20these%20were%20people%20who%20came%20forward%20volunteering%20to%20conduct%20literacy%20classes%20for%20the%20adults.%20In%20the%20bargain%2C%20we%20also%20made%20them%20agents%20of%20peace.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20songs%20composed%20in%20tribal%20dialect%20to%20peace%20committee%20meetings%2C%20a%20proper%20plan%20was%20instated.%20And%2C%20in%20nine%20months%2C%20the%20violence%20gave%20way%20to%20peace.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20was%20a%20demand%20for%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F449043%2Ftwo-women-yuva-madhavi-teaching-school-dropouts-street-children-hyderabad-chotuu-ki-education%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egood%20quality%20school%20education%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20Jhingran%20shares%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20people%20demanded%20that%20schools%20improve%2C%20teachers%20attend%20school%20regularly%2C%20that%20school%20building%20infrastructure%20be%20improved%2C%20and%20children%20actually%20learn.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20district%20authorities%20remarked%20on%20the%20campaign%E2%80%99s%20success.%20Uddalak%20Datta%2C%20part%20of%20the%20Assam%20civil%20service%20and%20an%20extra%20assistant%20commissioner%20(EAC)%20of%20Kokrajhar%20at%20the%20time%2C%20shares%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20had%20never%20imagined%20that%20something%20so%20transformational%20could%20happen%20in%20the%20system.%20Kokrajhar%20district%20was%20affected%20by%20extremism.%20People%20were%20so%20scared%2C%20no%20one%20wanted%20to%20stay%20there%20because%20of%20the%20violence.%20But%20Jhingran%20transformed%20their%20mindsets.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20continues%2C%20%E2%80%9CJhingran%20inspired%20everyone.%20He%20involved%20everyone.%20He%20saw%20who%20could%20work%20in%20which%20department%20of%20the%20campaign.%20People%20found%20a%20leader%20who%20could%20really%20motivate%20them%20and%20mobilise%20them.%20It%20was%20such%20a%20grand%20success%20in%20terms%20of%20a%20vibrant%20campaign.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20success%20of%20the%20campaign%20affirmed%20Jhingran%E2%80%99s%20faith%20in%20the%20strategy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EAn%20antidote%20to%20educational%20precarity%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20of%20what%20is%20taught%20to%20a%20child%20cannot%20fit%20into%20the%20binary%20of%20their%20native%20language%20and%20the%20mode%20of%20instruction%20in%20school%20(often%20English).%20This%20isn%E2%80%99t%20just%20Jhingran%E2%80%99s%20reasoning%3B%20the%20view%20is%20also%20shared%20by%20the%20United%20Nations.%20A%20UN%20article%2C%20estimating%20that%20at%20least%20half%20of%20the%20global%20population%20is%20bilingual%2C%20called%20for%20%E2%80%9Cmother%20language-based%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F400360%2Fmahmood-akram-languages-youth-world-record-prodigy%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emultilingual%20education%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20fundamental%20to%20achieving%20quality%2C%20inclusive%20learning%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20underscored%20that%20students%20learn%20best%20in%20a%20language%20they%20understand%2C%20and%20that%20children%20who%20speak%20the%20language%20they%20are%20taught%20in%20are%2014%20percent%20more%20likely%20to%20read%20with%20understanding%20at%20the%20end%20of%20primary%2C%20compared%20to%20those%20who%20do%20not.%20But%20the%20irony%2C%20the%20report%20highlighted%2C%20is%20that%20%E2%80%9C40%20percent%20of%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20population%20does%20no