a.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FRajib-Assam-5-1752485297-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-469458%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EHomestays%20in%20Saraipung%2C%20built%20from%20local%20materials%2C%20offer%20tourists%20a%20unique%20glimpse%20into%20Assam%E2%80%99s%20natural%20and%20cultural%20heritage.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFrom%20hunters%20to%20hosts%2C%20bows%20to%20binoculars%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERajib%20also%20identified%20a%20critical%20need%20%E2%80%94%20a%20sustainable%20alternative%20to%20hunting%20that%20spoke%20to%20both%20the%20villagers%E2%80%99%20hearts%20and%20their%20wallets.%20Enter%20eco-tourism%2C%20a%20novel%20concept%20to%20the%20villagers%20but%20one%20filled%20with%20potential.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGradually%2C%20homestays%20emerged%20amid%20the%20trees%2C%20offering%20visitors%20a%20chance%20to%20experience%20the%20serenity%20and%20biodiversity%20that%20had%20been%20preserved.%20These%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F392966%2Fsustainable-homestays-responsible-tourism-vacation-weekend-getaways-travel%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3D1.%2CRead%2520more%2520here.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehomestays%20are%20constructed%20in%20traditional%20styles%20%3C%2Fa%3Eand%20provide%20an%20authentic%20experience%20of%20living%20close%20to%20nature.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETourists%2C%20including%20international%20visitors%2C%20are%20accommodated%20in%20homestays%20that%20offer%20a%20unique%20local%20experience.%20When%20tourists%20arrive%2C%20they%20are%20welcomed%20into%20the%20heart%20of%20Assamese%20hospitality%2C%20savouring%20traditional%20meals%20cooked%20with%20local%20greens.%20One%20notable%20dish%20is%20rice%20cooked%20in%20bamboo.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECultural%20programs%20and%20traditional%20dances%20are%20organised%2C%20giving%20tourists%20a%20